@UPS - A scandal !!!
Hi friends a precious advice: avoid UPS
4 months ago i choosed UPS to ensure a delivery from France to Ireland, a big mistake !
- a TV broken on the top
- 1 month to be at last delivered
- an overbilling
My TV costed 1700€ and they don't want to refund me
